---

<Base title="R. Mocci - Shoutouts - Ian Hogers" side="neutral">
  <section class="py-6">
    <p class="font-mono text-sm mb-6">
      <a href="/shoutouts" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white no-underline">‚Üê back to shoutouts</a>
    </p>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
      <span class="text-4xl">üè≥Ô∏è</span>
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl text-cyan-400 mb-0">R. Mocci</h1>
        <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-500">Tiny Archive ¬∑ CC0 pixel art</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pixel-box p-6 mb-8" style="--box-color: #22d3ee;">
      <div class="prose">
        <p><strong class="text-cyan-400">Rob</strong> builds a growing library of CC0 and OFL resources. Pixel art, fonts, sounds. Tools of choice: Inkscape, Ableton, FontForge, sometimes Blender. All of it released freely for anyone to use.</p>

        <p>We use his pixel flag assets on the <a href="/skills" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">skills grid</a>. He has packs covering the Americas, Asia/Oceania, Africa, Europe, USA, and Archipelagos. All CC0, no strings attached.</p>

        <p>The license says no credit required. We do it anyway because that is the right thing to do. People who put good work into the commons deserve to be seen.</p>

        <h2 class="text-cyan-400">Find Rob</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://rmocci.itch.io/" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">itch.io</a> - flag packs and other pixel art</li>
          <li><a href="https://patreon.com/rmocci" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Patreon</a> - support the work</li>
          <li><a href="https://mastodon.social/@avreference" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Mastodon</a> - @avreference</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-600 font-mono">
      <span class="star-sprite w-4 h-4 animate-sparkle opacity-40" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span>CC0 is a gift. Thank you, Rob.</span>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
